OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalian football fan banned
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor 'slapping' journalist  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Flive on TV                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italian police have banned a football  
OL,6, fan from sporting events for three     
OL,7, years after he allegedly slapped the   
OL,8, bottom of a female reporter live on TV.
OL,10,FThe man was filmed moving his hand     
OL,11,Ftowards Greta Beccaglia as she faced   
OL,12,Fthe camera after a Serie A football    
OL,13,Fmatch in Florence.                     
OL,15,FThe incident on Saturday prompted anger
OL,16,Fand solidarity with the reporter.      
OL,18,FMs Beccaglia of Toscana TV filed a     
OL,19,Fharassment complaint against the man,  
OL,20,Fwho is under police investigation.     
